# HTGAA Bio-Bootcamp Day 1

## Date: Tuesday, January 19th, 2026 9 AM \- 12 AM EST

This handout is an overview about the topics we will cover on the first day of Bio-Bootcamp and resources that you can explore ahead of or following the Bio-Bootcamp.

## Summary

In this part of the HTGAA BioBootcamp introduce basic concepts of biology, give an organizational overview about the Biobootcamp, including the onboarding process and introduce global projects that students may choose to participate in during the HTGAA course.
